Put the file "Psychiatric_hospital.vmf" into your:

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefabs

Run Source SDK with:

. Engine Version: Half-Life 2: Episode One;
. Current Game: Counter-Strike: Source.

Click on "File" than "Open" and navigate to your "prefabs" folder onto your C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefabs writed before.

P.S.: The name "psychiatric hospital" is beta...I'll change it soon to "Hospital Room". ^_^

Have FuN :D
